text: Phryneta ellioti is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1909. It is known from Uganda and the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Phryneta ellioti. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1909
